snippet.textDisplay: This. This. This is why my heart aches on partition. Had we stayed together, it would have been an altogether different story. I'm a proud Hindu and Indian and it sinks me to know that we can't call these singers as our own. Not long back, just 65 odd years back we bore same struggle and now we are just fighting over a piece of land. And both sides inclined to prove who is greater than other. It's like two kids trying to prove to their mother who is better than the other, India, Pakistan are two parts of one colonial India. We had so much together, so much for each other. So, many similar traditions. So, much! And now? :'(
